v 3
d belieffit: Stata command for fitting a two-equation belief model with fixed-point iteration
d
d belieffit estimates posterior mean log beliefs and corrects parametrically for bias from posterior variance.
d The command combines a corrected-mean equation and a PPML variance equation, iterating until the predicted variance stabilizes.
d
d Author: Martin Eckhoff Andresen, University of Oslo
d Repository: https://github.com/martin-andresen/belieffit
d Requires: reghdfe and ppmlhdfe
d
f belieffit.ado
f belieffit.sthlp
